    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"Hi Friends üëã, Welcome To aGuideHub! ‚ù§Ô∏è In this article, we will use some bootstrap classes to design responsive background image. To make background image‚Ä¶","html":"<p>Hi Friends üëã,</p>\n<p>Welcome To aGuideHub! ‚ù§Ô∏è</p>\n<p>In this article, we will use some bootstrap classes to design responsive background image.</p>\n<p>To make background image responsive, put <code class=\"language-text\">background-size: 100% 100%; and background-repeat: no-repeat</code> class to create background image responsive in bootstrap.</p>\n<p>Table of contents</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Includes bootstrap view</li>\n<li>Includes bootstrap library</li>\n<li>Includes css in html page</li>\n<li>Define its class name</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Step 1: Includes bootstrap view</h3>\n<p>To ensure proper rendering and touch zooming for all devices, add the responsive viewport meta tag to your <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;head></code>.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">name</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>viewport<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">content</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>Step 2: Includes bootstrap library</h3>\n<p>First of all, load the Bootstrap framework CSS into the head tag of your webpage.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Bootstrap CSS --></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>link</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">rel</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>stylesheet<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> </code></pre></div>\n<h3>Step 3: Includes css in html page</h3>\n<p>Here we are using in css class to create background image.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\">     <span class=\"token selector\">.bg-image</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> \n    <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> \n    <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 600px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> \n    <span class=\"token property\">background-image</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string url\">'image/background-image.jpg'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> \n    <span class=\"token property\">background-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100% 100%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n    <span class=\"token property\">background-repeat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> no-repeat<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> </code></pre></div>\n<h3>Step 4: Define its class name</h3>\n<p>After that, create background image responsive with a class name <code class=\"language-text\">.bg-image</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>bg-image<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> </code></pre></div>\n<h3>Example.</h3>\n<p>Let‚Äôs look at the following example to understand how it basically works:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">DOCTYPE</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> \n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> \n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> \n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">name</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>viewport<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">content</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>link</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">rel</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>stylesheet<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> \n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\"> \n<span class=\"token selector\">.bg-image</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> \n    <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> \n    <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 600px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> \n    <span class=\"token property\">background-image</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string url\">'image/background-image.jpg'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> \n    <span class=\"token property\">background-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100% 100%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n    <span class=\"token property\">background-repeat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> no-repeat<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> \n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> \n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> \n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> \n\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>bg-image<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> \n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> \n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> </code></pre></div>\n<p>Check the output of the above code example.</p>\n<p><strong><em>when window size is > 576px :</em></strong></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1023e4288b7dc7724f04fe42b136f6e9/38f6f/background-image.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 49.36708860759494%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Bootstrap, Table, Responsive\"\n        title=\"Bootstrap, Table, Responsive\"\n        src=\"/static/1023e4288b7dc7724f04fe42b136f6e9/828fb/background-image.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1023e4288b7dc7724f04fe42b136f6e9/ff44c/background-image.jpg 158w,\n/static/1023e4288b7dc7724f04fe42b136f6e9/a6688/background-image.jpg 315w,\n/static/1023e4288b7dc7724f04fe42b136f6e9/828fb/background-image.jpg 630w,\n/static/1023e4288b7dc7724f04fe42b136f6e9/0ede0/background-image.jpg 945w,\n/static/1023e4288b7dc7724f04fe42b136f6e9/3ac88/background-image.jpg 1260w,\n/static/1023e4288b7dc7724f04fe42b136f6e9/38f6f/background-image.jpg 1366w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><strong><em>When window size  is less than &#x3C; 576px :</em></strong></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d26e275d68f3efe1aa9cfa77ce7cbe8a/38f6f/background-image1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 46.835443037974684%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Bootstrap, Table, Responsive\"\n        title=\"Bootstrap, Table, Responsive\"\n        src=\"/static/d26e275d68f3efe1aa9cfa77ce7cbe8a/828fb/background-image1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d26e275d68f3efe1aa9cfa77ce7cbe8a/ff44c/background-image1.jpg 158w,\n/static/d26e275d68f3efe1aa9cfa77ce7cbe8a/a6688/background-image1.jpg 315w,\n/static/d26e275d68f3efe1aa9cfa77ce7cbe8a/828fb/background-image1.jpg 630w,\n/static/d26e275d68f3efe1aa9cfa77ce7cbe8a/0ede0/background-image1.jpg 945w,\n/static/d26e275d68f3efe1aa9cfa77ce7cbe8a/3ac88/background-image1.jpg 1260w,\n/static/d26e275d68f3efe1aa9cfa77ce7cbe8a/38f6f/background-image1.jpg 1366w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>All the best üëç</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"How to make background image responsive in bootstrap?","tags":["Bootstrap"],"date":"June 14, 2022","description":"Example of make background image responsive in bootstrap with step by step tutorial - aGuideHub","social_image":"media/template/bootstrap.jpg"}},"prev":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to make button text bold in bootstrap 4?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/how-to-make-button-text-bold-in-bootstrap-4/"}},"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to make card responsive in bootstrap?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/how-to-make-card-responsive-in-bootstrap/"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/how-to-make-background-image-responsive-in-bootstrap/","prevSlug":"/blog/how-to-make-button-text-bold-in-bootstrap-4/","nextSlug":"/blog/how-to-make-card-responsive-in-bootstrap/"}},
